{
  "text": "Medicare provides support to all sectors of the health system, paying physicians either directly or indirectly on a fee for service basis. Under Medicare, physicians can also refer patients for a range of proscribed health services delivered by allied health professionals [CITATION_1] . These services are limited to specific conditions and patients and clearly described in regulations.",
